<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><refentry version="5.0-subset Scilab" xml:id="dnn_zoo_modelinfo" xml:lang="en_US" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"><refnamediv><refname>dnn_zoo_modelinfo</refname><refpurpose>Return IPCV hints for OpenCV Zoo model families.</refpurpose></refnamediv><refsynopsisdiv><title>Syntax</title><synopsis>info = dnn_zoo_modelinfo(modelName)
info = dnn_zoo_modelinfo(modelName, groupName)</synopsis></refsynopsisdiv><refsection><title>Arguments</title><variablelist><varlistentry><term>modelName</term><listitem><para>OpenCV Zoo model file name.</para></listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term>groupName</term><listitem><para>Optional OpenCV Zoo model category folder.</para></listitem></varlistentry><varlistentry><term>info</term><listitem><para>Structure containing task, inputSize, scale, mean, swapRB, crop, decoder, and notes fields.</para></listitem></varlistentry></variablelist></refsection><refsection><title>Description</title><para><literal>dnn_zoo_modelinfo</literal> provides practical IPCV defaults for common OpenCV Zoo model families. It is used by the OpenCV Zoo GUI to generate more useful sample scripts.</para></refsection><refsection><title>Examples</title><programlisting><![CDATA[info = dnn_zoo_modelinfo("image_classification_mobilenetv2_2022apr.onnx", "image_classification_mobilenet");
disp(info.task)
disp(info.inputSize)
]]></programlisting></refsection><refsection><title>See Also</title><simplelist type="inline"><member><link linkend="dnn_forward">dnn_forward</link></member><member><link linkend="dnn_decode_classification">dnn_decode_classification</link></member><member><link linkend="dnn_decode_yolo">dnn_decode_yolo</link></member><member><link linkend="dnn_decode_segmentation">dnn_decode_segmentation</link></member><member><link linkend="opencv_zoo_gui">opencv_zoo_gui</link></member></simplelist></refsection><refsection><title>Authors</title><simplelist type="vert"><member>Tan Chin Luh</member></simplelist></refsection><refsection><title>History</title><informaltable border="1"><tr><td><emphasis role="bold">Version</emphasis></td><td><emphasis role="bold">Description</emphasis></td></tr><tr><td>5.0.0</td><td>Function introduced.</td></tr></informaltable></refsection></refentry>
